{"tid":1165086,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"美國：中國製造無人機資料或落入第三方","createTime":"2019-05-21T14:28:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T16:04:22.000Z","uid":225846,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d9bbfa17be7c61b762ff03fc75bc877958dc96c2","tid":1165086,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T14:28:41.000Z","msg":"【美國：中國製造無人機資料或落入第三方】<br />\n【大疆：產品數據完全由用戶掌握】<br />\n　　<br />\n美國政府警告當地企業，中國製造無人機獲取的敏感資料，可能會落在第三方，包括中國政府手上，提醒業界注意。<br />\n　　<br />\n警示未有點名提及個別製造商，但指連同中國的情報監控行動，兩者對美國企業的資訊構成威脅，涉及國安及關鍵技術範疇的企業須警惕，可能有更大風險遭遇黑客攻擊及竊取資訊。<br />\n　　<br />\n現時接近八成在美國及加拿大出售的無人機均來自總部設於深圳的DJI大疆創新。大疆創新發表聲明稱高度重視信息安全，產品的安全性得到華府和美國企業反覆及獨立驗證，強調產品數據完全由用戶掌握。<br />\n　　<br />\n#有線新聞 #無人機 #大彊DJI #獲取敏感資料<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1115175148674552/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F186040714921338%2Fposts%2F1115175148674552%2F&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TSlZyh30VB0jKt3ffwT98zY%3D&h=87f00244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1115175148674552/</a>"},{"pid":"3127cc52c7cbe52522501faa81387ec65e6d7da7","tid":1165086,"uid":79077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T14:29:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e8c86c42f6d3a89b8680f50215c247f458073dd9","tid":1165086,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3127cc52c7cbe52522501faa81387ec65e6d7da7","tid":1165086,"uid":79077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T14:29:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T14:30:51.000Z","msg":"幾時俾人拉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe85500f62e2c987822c7c17c8b315612fbb4b3","tid":1165086,"uid":189911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T14:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Q5Uihc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Q5Uih